### Signal Logic Detail

#### Layer 1 — Data Sources

| Data Source | Signal | McPCG Tool | Priority |
|---|---|---|---|
| CoinGlass | SpotCVD | `coinglass_spot_cvd` | **#1 HARD VETO** |
| CoinGlass | FutCVD | `coinglass_futures_cvd` | **#2 HARD VETO** |
| CoinGlass | Liquidation | `coinglass_liquidation_cat` | #3 Confluence |
| CoinGlass | Open Interest | `coinglass_open_interest_cat` | #4 Confirmation |
| CoinGlass | Taker Volume | `coinglass_futures_taker_cat` | #5 Confirmation |
| Binance WS | Price Feed | `bookTicker` stream | Execution timing |
| Binance WS | Order Book | `depth` stream | Entry precision |

#### Layer 2 — Signal Engine Checks

| Check | Logic |
|---|---|
| **1. SpotCVD Gate** | Harus POSITIF dan sustained 3+ candles. Single flip = REJECT. Hard veto. |
| **2. FutCVD Alignment** | Harus align dengan SpotCVD. Divergence = hedging signal = REJECT. |
| **3. Liquidation Confluence** | Arah liquidation harus confirm direction. |
| **4. OI + Taker** | OI rising + Taker buy dominant = genuine bias. Harus confirm. |
| **5. Scoring** | Score ≥ 90 = full size. ≥ 80 = 75%. ≥ 70 = 50%. < 70 = REJECT. |

#### Layer 3 — State Manager Rules

| Check | Rule |
|---|---|
| Posisi aktif? | Ada open position di pair yang sama → BLOCK |
| Max positions | > 3 concurrent → BLOCK |
| Cooldown | 5 menit setelah close → BLOCK |
| Daily drawdown | ≥ 3% dari modal → STOP semua |

#### Layer 4 — Execution Rules

| Komponen | Detail |
|---|---|
| Order type | Market order entry (speed priority) |
| SL/TP | Langsung set setelah fill. SL = -1.5%, TP = +3% (2:1 RR) |
| Partial fill | Tunggu 2s → cek lagi → kalau partial → cancel sisa |
| Retry | Network error → 3x retry: 1s, 2s, 4s backoff |
| Stale signal | Signal > 10 detik → cancel, jangan execute |

